Tere bina zindagi hai jaise raat bina chaand ke,
Tum ho mere dil ki, zaroorat har ek aandhe ke.

Tere husn ki chamak hai jaise chaandani raat,
Tum ho meri zindagi ki, khoobsurat sabse baat.

Tere saath har pal hai jaise khushboo se bhar jaaye,
Umaimah, tu meri duniya, sapno ko sajaaye.

Tere bina zindagi hai ek veeran raaste ki tarah,
Tum hi ho mere dil ki raahat, chaah har raah ki yahaan.

Teri muskurahat se roshan meri duniya ki raat,
Tum ho meri khushi ka rang, zindagi ki baat.

Tere khwabon se roshan hai meri zindagi ki raah,
Tum ho mere sapnon ka asar, mere har ek aashiq baah.



